  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your family,  blacksmiths for generations, harbors an age-old ambition—to forge the ultimate weapon and be the best blacksmith. The key to this legendary creation lies in the Abyss, a fabled realm beneath the earth that holds the rarest mystical materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must manage your mining operation, collect resources, and craft items to sell for profit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your mining tools and as you progress towards your goal, you can purchase better mining licences and delve deeper into the earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect mystical ancient relics to gain its power and boost your efficiency. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Purchase mining licences from different areas</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy higher tier licences and discover rarer minerals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/73195259fc07099d8cfbc2be18087300.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=644 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/73195259fc07099d8cfbc2be18087300.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/73195259fc07099d8cfbc2be18087300.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use your mining tools and gather raw materials</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the tools and adapt to the circumstances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/53f5f14c4fd994b9c7749f680f8c5b26.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=690 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/53f5f14c4fd994b9c7749f680f8c5b26.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/53f5f14c4fd994b9c7749f680f8c5b26.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Run your own shop; sell, haggle and build your fame</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize and boost your shop with several furnitures which you can find at mining sites.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/1505ff1c381ea54ab553ef83c14ab822.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=712 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/1505ff1c381ea54ab553ef83c14ab822.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/1505ff1c381ea54ab553ef83c14ab822.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Delve depper and deeper and find exotic resources</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you dig down the rarer minerals you will be able to mine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/af88560bca0894a95029a8e58fcc0f32.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=800 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/af88560bca0894a95029a8e58fcc0f32.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/af88560bca0894a95029a8e58fcc0f32.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock blueprints, craft and sell items for profit</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more exotic the item you craft, the more it sells for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/d875f0a5205773364bf0608415ebc706.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=628 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/d875f0a5205773364bf0608415ebc706.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/d875f0a5205773364bf0608415ebc706.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your mining operation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run your own shop, sell and haggle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your shop's fame and attract more customers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Market demand and supply system with dynamic market events. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig out and mine procedural mining sites to gather raw materials.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find old furnitures and reuse them in your shop to gain boosts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use several different mining tools, each has its own advantage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your tools to be more efficient and reach deeper layers to find rarer resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful relics and gain its power.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft items to sell for profit and progress towards your goal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock exotic blueprints and gain more reputation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh and don't forget to just chill and watch how the worm eat all the dirt.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your family,  blacksmiths for generations, harbors an age-old ambition—to forge the ultimate weapon and be the best blacksmith. The key to this legendary creation lies in the Abyss, a fabled realm beneath the earth that holds the rarest mystical materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must manage your mining operation, collect resources, and craft items to sell for profit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your mining tools and as you progress towards your goal, you can purchase better mining licences and delve deeper into the earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect mystical ancient relics to gain its power and boost your efficiency. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Purchase mining licences from different areas</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy higher tier licences and discover rarer minerals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/73195259fc07099d8cfbc2be18087300.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=644 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/73195259fc07099d8cfbc2be18087300.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/73195259fc07099d8cfbc2be18087300.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use your mining tools and gather raw materials</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the tools and adapt to the circumstances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/53f5f14c4fd994b9c7749f680f8c5b26.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=690 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/53f5f14c4fd994b9c7749f680f8c5b26.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/53f5f14c4fd994b9c7749f680f8c5b26.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Run your own shop; sell, haggle and build your fame</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize and boost your shop with several furnitures which you can find at mining sites.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/1505ff1c381ea54ab553ef83c14ab822.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=712 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/1505ff1c381ea54ab553ef83c14ab822.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/1505ff1c381ea54ab553ef83c14ab822.mp4?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Delve depper and deeper and find exotic resources</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you dig down the rarer minerals you will be able to mine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/af88560bca0894a95029a8e58fcc0f32.poster.avif?t=1763823974\" width=800 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452900/extras/af88560bca0894a95029a8e58fcc0f32.webm?t=1763823974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"htt